You will need the following:

Java SE
   A build tool. You can choose between:
Maven - version 3.3.1 or higher
Gradle
IntelliJ IDEA (which will be used in this tutorial)
   IntelliJ IDEA Cucumber for Java plugin
Eclipse (a good alternative if you donâ€™t use IntelliJ)
   Cucumber Eclipse - Plugin
   Natual - For Gherkins - Plugin
   





You can run following command:

mvn archetype:generate   "-DarchetypeGroupId=io.cucumber" "-DarchetypeArtifactId=cucumber-archetype"  "-DarchetypeVersion=7.0.0" "-DgroupId=hellocucumber" "-DartifactId=hellocucumber" "-Dpackage=hellocucumber" 
"-Dversion=1.0.0-SNAPSHOT" "-DinteractiveMode=false"




   

